```

This check at line 1859 in `statements.py` makes no sense.

```python
                when_ = ptr.search_one('when')
                if when_ is not None:
                    err_add(ctx.errors, when_.pos, 'KEY_HAS_DEFAULT', ())

```
"when" has nothing to do with `KEY_HAS_DEFAULT` error ("default value for a key leaf is ignored").

